< 3 min Goal Slicer and Grade Versatility Goal Slicer 24

Step 1: Create < 3 min Goal slicer

- Choose the slicer visual, insert the value from Number Table 2 in the field.

- Change the format of the value to a percentage

- Change from a slider formatted slicer to a drop down formatted slicer

- Select formatting and under general, X position = 217, Y position = 89, Width = 253, Height = 52




- Slicer Header off

- Title on = < 3min Goal, font color = black, alignment = center, text size = 8, font family = Constantia

- Background on = Color = Custom (AOD1FF)

- Border on = dark gray




Step 2: Create GV Goal Slicer

- Copy and Paste the < 3min Goal slicer, change out the field to Value in Number Table

- Select Formatting and under general X position = 505, Y position = 89, Width = 253, Height = 52

- Title should be changed to GV Versatility

- Change the format of value to a percentage

- Select 50.00% for < 3min Goal and select 35.00% for GV Goal.
